    <item>
      <title>温哥华市长提议在城市财政中使用比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/vancouver-mayor-proposes-integrating-bitcoin-btc-into-city-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当比特币这一数字代币的价值飙升之际，温哥华可能会尝试将其融入城市财政，而这一涨势受到美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对加密货币的支持的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/vancouver-mayor-proposes-integrating-bitcoin-btc-into-city-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命戴维·萨克斯为白宫人工智能和加密货币主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/trump-names-david-sacks-as-white-house-ai-and-crypto-czar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他正在选择 Craft Ventures LLC 的风险投资家戴维·萨克斯担任他的人工智能和加密沙皇，这个新设立的职位凸显了这位当选总统推动两个快速发展行业的意图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/trump-names-david-sacks-as-white-house-ai-and-crypto-czar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>短暂下跌后，比特币稳定在 10 万美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/bitcoin-btc-briefly-slumps-nearly-7-as-traders-hedge-for-pullback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币在当天早些时候短暂下跌近 7% 后，本周首次稳定在 100,000 美元以下，凸显出过去一个月上涨之后波动性加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/bitcoin-btc-briefly-slumps-nearly-7-as-traders-hedge-for-pullback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
